						<div class="postbody">Yeah you pretty much got it. Also a buffer is needed to have buffered writes (and possibly reads) to $2007 during VBlank. A buffered palette is aslo necessary. And it's best to come with a full sound engine which is able to play music and sound effects.</div>

					
